List of topics for NELSI tutorial
=================================

- Simulate a phylogenetic tree under a Yule speciation process

  - Plot tree with intenral node ages with branching times

- Simulate constant rate and explain tree.data.matrix

- Simulate autocorrelated with Kishino model

- Simulate uncorrelated with lognormal

- Simulate nucleotide sequences and write everything in an external file

- Load a virus tree from BEAST

  - Plot tree with ages of internal nodes and tips

- Get the tree data matrix

  - Plot rates with plot.ratesim

- Get root-to-tip regression data and plot
